{"tid":262348,"cid":21,"subCid":0,"title":"[學術討論]點解keyboard無E# B#","createTime":"2017-05-29T07:14:37.000Z","updateTime":"2017-05-29T17:06:00.000Z","uid":73724,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"c8b184c2eed162bd7b345683dc878aa56a10da7d","tid":262348,"uid":73724,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-29T07:14:37.000Z","msg":"我知道E#即係F，因為係一個半音。<br />\n但點解一開始做keyboard嘅人唔整做6個全音，而係全全半全全全半？<br />\n有講法係畢達哥拉斯嘅3/2理論？點做到十二音律出黎？<br />\n卡左喺呢個問題好耐<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ad8f93712e5f8c591984965dabc04842e7c46ee3","tid":262348,"uid":65072,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-29T07:18:24.000Z","msg":"整左你點搵中央C?"},{"pid":"f05a862ab0c7aac846b7739b6df69e11b0527d9e","tid":262348,"uid":62532,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-29T07:19:59.000Z","msg":"因為要跟so fa me"},{"pid":"a6efd4547f3cd5a014bd584c7a57201d2b1b09ed","tid":262348,"uid":67553,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-29T07:23:51.000Z","msg":"我估係一開始大概有個middle C咁嘅嘢做reference note，咁有十二平均律之後就以C做tonic咁整個major scale，所以依家嘅黑白鍵係咁排<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"48c9415e2ee37e040959ede9bb163b1c56b53418","tid":262348,"uid":56843,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-29T07:32:24.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/05/29/153150_11b0c7bc978725c95410d702ef50e27d.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F05%2F29%2F153150_11b0c7bc978725c95410d702ef50e27d.jpg&h=beba69f7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n之前都有諗過類似問題"},{"pid":"6b1d68741accd1b23769e72bda61ec84a3712f7e","tid":262348,"uid":73724,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-29T09:22:36.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>整左你點搵中央C?</blockquote><br />\n唔明"},{"pid":"a5cd7c685de838d2517d895175c5c06ec2b1d747","tid":262348,"uid":73724,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-29T09:23:09.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>我估係一開始大概有個middle C咁嘅嘢做reference note，咁有十二平均律之後就以C做tonic咁整個major scale，所以依家嘅黑白鍵係咁排<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n講多啲？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"53e50fc79eb386d4406f8fbcd56333a6e28791c1","tid":262348,"uid":73724,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-29T09:46:59.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><img src=\"http://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/05/29/153150_11b0c7bc978725c95410d702ef50e27d.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F05%2F29%2F153150_11b0c7bc978725c95410d702ef50e27d.jpg&h=beba69f7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n之前都有諗過類似問題</blockquote><br />\n我諗我唔係呢個意思。我意思係點解無E# B#，應該唔係調式問題<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/37.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5528b593445201efa3fdadbe42c18af9cceb405f","tid":262348,"uid":90596,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-29T09:59:06.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><img src=\"http://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/05/29/153150_11b0c7bc978725c95410d702ef50e27d.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F05%2F29%2F153150_11b0c7bc978725c95410d702ef50e27d.jpg&h=beba69f7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n之前都有諗過類似問題</blockquote><br />\n我諗我唔係呢個意思。我意思係點解無E# B#，應該唔係調式問題<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/37.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n係咪則係問點解唔係一個英文字母代表一全度<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\nA A# B C C# D D# E F F# G G# A 點解唔寫做<br />\nA A# B B# C C# D D# E E# F F# A<br />\n係咪咁嘅意思<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"50d1fecbb2a4181fdd5ca29fe8e079f72d6c9a79","tid":262348,"uid":73724,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-29T10:01:29.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>整左你點搵中央C?</blockquote><br />\n唔明</blockquote><br />\n我明你講咩啦。<br />\n或者咁講，結他都無寫Abc，但你都可以記得/通過中間嘅點點去知道邊個係咩音。<br />\n如果一開始就係六個全音，人類就應該會加點點去令大家分辨，所以不成問題。"},{"pid":"bb95fde207fc1b395e297d6faef0de291b637b99","tid":262348,"uid":73724,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-29T10:02:46.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><img src=\"http://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/05/29/153150_11b0c7bc978725c95410d702ef50e27d.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F05%2F29%2F153150_11b0c7bc978725c95410d702ef50e27d.jpg&h=beba69f7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n之前都有諗過類似問題</blockquote><br />\n我諗我唔係呢個意思。我意思係點解無E# B#，應該唔係調式問題<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/37.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n係咪則係問點解唔係一個英文字母代表一全度<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\nA A# B C C# D D# E F F# G G# A 點解唔寫做<br />\nA A# B B# C C# D D# E E# F F# A<br />\n係咪咁嘅意思<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n可以咁理解嘅<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"740f4e8f81f049c0e42edb4fd6f582c45ad8f92c","tid":262348,"uid":52991,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-29T10:18:48.000Z","msg":"我覺得係有堆人定左係咁，會覺得7個冇sharp冇flat加5個black keys既會比較易明同埋冇咁覆雜。而既E#同B#係物理世界入面其實係會同F,C唔同音，係equal temperament 之前d人係聽兩粒音既同嗚而去tune (overtunes series?), 每一粒音既根音同佢既partial去tune,所以以前d 人tune 好左c key之後去彈其他 key就會走曬音。 同埋B#同E#呢兩粒音唔實用，B#同E# 既major scale都會有double sharps ，而有double sharps既scale都只係理論上既野，極之少用。"},{"pid":"2a652c1c89d7028e02d6e3210e793572636b6acb","tid":262348,"uid":397,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-29T10:46:15.000Z","msg":"無記錯12粒音係用條式除出黎<br />\n由middle c 開始 係咁除唔知幾多又三份一<br />\n除哂白鍵7粒音出黎<br />\n之後古人覺得唔夠玩 推出一個8度再除多次<br />\n強行將除完個個frequency 拉返低做middle c個個8度既range 變成左黑鍵<br />\n<br />\n好似係"},{"pid":"bccdd2fabf30ecfcbe2d45eb5b0686edcc1fc73e","tid":262348,"uid":73724,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-29T11:44:24.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>無記錯12粒音係用條式除出黎<br />\n由middle c 開始 係咁除唔知幾多又三份一<br />\n除哂白鍵7粒音出黎<br />\n之後古人覺得唔夠玩 推出一個8度再除多次<br />\n強行將除完個個frequency 拉返低做middle c個個8度既range 變成左黑鍵<br />\n<br />\n好似係</blockquote><br />\n係呀，我都有研究得到。A係440hz，而由A開始不斷乘三除二，每過880hz會再除二，會得到12個hz，即係：<br />\nA A# B C C# D D# E F F# G G#，<br />\n即係現代嘅12音。<br />\n<br />\n但一開始頭7音(即頭七次乘三除二)嘅hz，係現代嘅：<br />\nA B C# D# E F# G#。<br />\n正常人都唔會一開始發明到一舊野就加#，所以就算係我寫，我都會寫ABCDEFG。<br />\n<br />\n唯有由F開始計，先會得到<br />\nF G A B C D E <br />\n<br />\n點解會咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c3cd4e00d485616b4214625b767d399486297e25","tid":262348,"uid":55511,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-29T12:22:14.000Z","msg":"聽聞E# =/= F"},{"pid":"4b65f233cc45537ef3211c042c2e849b89804b53","tid":262348,"uid":397,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-29T13:19:01.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>聽聞E# =/= F</blockquote><br />\n定義上 function上唔同<br />\n但hz一樣"},{"pid":"f2ce76cc9460524dad7a8479b561ae76c58be2b4","tid":262348,"uid":73724,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-29T13:32:24.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>聽聞E# =/= F</blockquote><br />\n定義上 function上唔同<br />\n但hz一樣</blockquote><br />\n無錯 所以其實唔太影響討論"},{"pid":"28727ec63ea8d72ebc64914074d53b550e2c5c6c","tid":262348,"uid":52991,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-29T14:53:21.000Z","msg":"咪話E#同B#唔實用所以冇囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n同埋只有係equal temperament上, B#同C, E#同F 先會一樣frequency，同埋現代有equal temperament，整多粒B#同E#都冇意思<br />\n<br />\n同埋你要既E#同B#琴，其實係有人整過既，叫Archicembalo"},{"pid":"6d2cd7003d7d8ee725e8693e95503e247164b5a8","tid":262348,"uid":52991,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-29T16:20:55.000Z","msg":"同埋以前既似會因應唔同Keys去tune，唔會次次用A = 440，況且以前都唔係440。C Major會用C 既根音開始tune。 Eb用Eb開始tune。 <br />\n到最後如果in C# major既話，佢既7音就係B#。<br />\n亦即係話你係鋼琴見到既C就係B# 。但係都個句，係equal temperament下，12粒音都平均分開左12，先會出現E#同F同hz。到下一步，你問緊既問題亦可以問點解冇Fb同Cb。其實呢個亦咁多年黎物理學家同音樂學家解決緊既問題，因為冇一個tuning 可以彈曬咁多個key直至有唔用既temperament出現。 到最後又可能引申到一個問題，點解係12個音唔係更多既音。我相信呢個同文化/歷史有關，話曬音樂係歐洲係當時發展得最好，好多出名既作曲家都跟呢套系統作曲。"},{"pid":"e150a2352420d699404da5b2269c3c79d062e5e2","tid":262348,"uid":66178,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-29T16:56:29.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://cps-static.rovicorp.com/3/JPG_400/MI0003/738/MI0003738578.jpg?partner=allrovi.com\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fcps-static.rovicorp.com%2F3%2FJPG_400%2FMI0003%2F738%2FMI0003738578.jpg%3Fpartner%3Dallrovi.com&h=d8936fca&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n     <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />    <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"86f28abf5df0807531dd492bd9d9200eb4fdacad","tid":262348,"uid":52991,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-29T17:06:00.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>同埋以前既似會因應唔同Keys去tune，唔會次次用A = 440，況且以前都唔係440。C Major會用C 既根音開始tune。 Eb用Eb開始tune。 <br />\n到最後如果in C# major既話，佢既7音就係B#。<br />\n亦即係話你係鋼琴見到既C就係B# 。但係都個句，係equal temperament下，12粒音都平均分開左12，先會出現E#同F同hz。到下一步，你問緊既問題亦可以問點解冇Fb同Cb。其實呢個亦咁多年黎物理學家同音樂學家解決緊既問題，因為冇一個tuning 可以彈曬咁多個key直至有唔<span style=\"color: red;\">同</span>既temperament出現。 到最後又可能引申到一個問題，點解係12個音唔係更多既音。我相信呢個同文化/歷史有關，話曬音樂係歐洲係當時發展得最好，好多出名既作曲家都跟呢套系統作曲。</blockquote>"}]}